fields.name: Helmet
fields.description: Cricket helmet for batsmen, Weighs approximatley 940 Gms. including a new improved fixed grill for increased safety. Increased facial & side protection. Removable and washable sweatband. Confirms to Latest ICC/BS 2013 safety standards including the back extention for more safety.

fields.name: Cricket Bat
fields.description: With an aggressive powerful profile and smouldering black graphics the Shadow is the ideal choice for the player who likes to make thing happen on the field. The addition of the new ‘Counterbalance’ handle enhances the ‘pick up’ to provide a bat which packs a heavyweight punch.

fields.name: Cricket Top
fields.description: A fantastically strong shirt that will stand up to the rigours of the cricket season. The Matrix shirt is as breathable as possible, ensuring cricketers young and old will keep cool even in the hottest conditions. In the modern game, with players become increasingly athletic and moving more dynamically, it was crucial that all Gray Nicolls cricket shirts were ergonomically designed.

fields.name: Cricket Bottom
fields.description: Professional quality garment. Moisture management and wicking materials with airflow to keep players cool. A supportive rib material which is used for the yoke and back panel of the leg give these trousers a modern, comfortable fit. Supplied with ivory trim only.

fields.name: Cricket Cap
fields.description: Designed to fit all head sizes, we've made the Melton Cap with an elasticated headband that gives the user a secure and comfortable fit, giving you peace of mind when are diving for the ball.

fields.name: Cricket Box
fields.description: Masuri Jockstrap with box is designed to hold the protective box to place under the whites and leave you to focus on more important things at the crease.

fields.name: Football Top
fields.description: Puma short sleeve training top with dry cell technology, Printed branding. 100% polyester. Crew neck. Straight hem.

fields.name: Football
fields.description: Emulate your heroes on the pitch with this Nike Strike Premier League Football which is ready for everyday play and features a high-contrast graphic design which allows you to track the the ball with ease. The ball has Nike Aerowtrac grooves which delivers an accurate ball flight right off the foot, whilst the textured casing helps enhance control and the balls 12-panels are machine stitched for long-lasting durability.

fields.name: Ladies Helmet
fields.description: Adjustable for all sizes, Factory fitted 360 faceguard. Robust ABS outer shell. Size adjustment dial. Superior ventilation system.

fields.name: Ladies Cricket Top
fields.description: The New Balance England Test Shirt is the perfect option for showcasing your support. Constructed with a three button placket, short sleeves and a fold over collar for a classic polo. The branding at the arm and team badge at the chest complete the sporty look.

fields.name: Stumps with Bails
fields.description: Made From Finest Quality Hardwood. Spring Return Stumps are natural wooden stumps with strong cast iron base and heavy duty spring return mechanism.

fields.name: White Cricket Ball
fields.description: Hand stitched 4-piece construction with 4 Layer quilted centre, Waxed and finished to English requirements, selected hide cover

fields.name: Cricket Gloves
fields.description: The Libro batting glove offers the highest levels of protection and comfort. Fully articulated with aptimum ventilation in palm areas.

fields.name: Cricket Thigh Gaurd
fields.description: Contoured thigh guard with extra large inner thigh pad creates an all in one lower body protection system. Combination of high density foam for lightweight, high impact protection, Adjustable elastic straps ensure a custom and comfortable fit

fields.name: Cricket Arm Gaurd
fields.description: The Arm Guard will absorb impact and stave off what would potentially be painful blows. The Premium PU Cover ensures the durability of the arm guard while maintaining its lightweight performance. The arm guard's towel backing works hard to absorb all moisture that can be generated when batting for long periods under intense pressure. Fitted with a stretchy strap, the arm guard is fully adjustable for a comfortable fit.

fields.name: Cricket Bag
fields.description: The main storage compartment is big enough to fit in the vast majority of your playing kit, essential for someone that has a lot of gear. Your pads and gloves will fit comfortably in here, with all your other internal protection. There’s an internal bat storage sleeve to keep your pride and joy as protected as possible.

fields.name: Batting Pads
fields.description: The tri-system vertical shin bolster offers fantastic coverage across the lower leg, where full, fast deliveries can have serious impact. The HD foam and cane rod combination give great coverage across the front of the batting pad, with lightweight protection which will never compromise your performance or speed across the ground. Again, this batting pad protection is supremely lightweight, with no impact on movement.

fields.name: Wickets Keeping Gloves
fields.description: The Prestige WicketKeeping gloves are a high class, high-performance glove that has been designed and refined by our product team in Robertsbridge. Sitting within the Classic range, the Prestige ooze class with their predominantly white colourway.

fields.name: Cricket Sweater Half Sleeve
fields.description: This classic cable-knit vest is updated with long-staple cotton and stripes in the tournament's traditional hues.

fields.name: Cricket Sweater Full Sleeve
fields.description: Readers Long Sleeved Sweater- produced from high quality durable heavyweight cable knit pattern.

fields.name: Cricket Blazer
fields.description: It feautures an internal zip pocket for security, a single back vent, suit style pockets and is stain resistant. It is also made from re-vive 100% recycled outer blazer fabric.

fields.name: Cricket Coat
fields.description: Breathable weather protection that optimises body temperature and keeps athletes at peak performance even in wind and rain by acting as a barrier to the elements while allowing heat and sweat to escape through evaporation. Cricket specific fit engineered to move naturally with the body.

fields.name: Football Goal
fields.description: Made from 42mm PVC tube this goal is strong to stand their best shots. Folding structure allows you to fold in secs. It's easy to take-away and saves space in the warehouse. Ground pegs included for playing on soft ground.

fields.name: Football Bag
fields.description: Precision budget team kit bag, Made from tough and durable PVC. Reinforced base with four stud feet. Zip closure with two carry handles, Ideal for carrying around all your sports kit

fields.name: Goalkeeper Gloves
fields.description: Features a flat palm cut, a Zohonero latex and an EVA backhand. Conventional elasticated strap with pull loop

fields.name: Football Air Pump
fields.description: Don't let a flat spoil your fun. Whether you're on the five-aside court, training field or pitch, this air pump ensures your football stays fully inflated. It has a dual action design, which means it inflates both on the push and pull.

fields.name: Football Shin Pads
fields.description: Shin Guards absorb impacts while keeping you comfortable. You can play your game with complete confidence thanks to the attached ankle guards. The straps ensure everything stays exactly where you need it to be.

fields.name: Football Free Kick Mannequin
fields.description: Moulded plastic chest plates and steel tubes. Ideal for evasion training or free kick practice, For use on grass,Ideal for club use - ideally slots into the ground as sold

fields.name: Portable Goals
fields.description: The Portable Goals are perfect for recreational play and small matches, complete with a handy carry bag for easy transportation and storage. This Goal Set includes 2 goal nets, easy to erect and set up with pegs securing them to the ground.

fields.name: Ball Bag
fields.description: This ball bag is great for storing away footballs and carrying them to sessions, with a drawstring fastening that also acts as a handle for you to carry the bag on your shoulder. The football sack has mesh panels so you can see the balls inside as well.

fields.name: England Top

fields.name: Liverpool Top
fields.description: Dress like the pros on match days with this LFC Match Home Shirt for the 21/22 season which benefits from being engineered with Dri-FIT ADV technology which provides you the perfect combination of lightweight cooling, reduced cling, a precision fit and moisture-wicking comfort to help keep you feeling fresh and fast for the entire 90 minutes.

fields.name: Football Shorts
fields.description: The Dry Training Shorts feature an elasticated waistband and drawstring fastening for a secure fit and are crafted from a lightweight Dry fabric with Dri-Fit to wick sweat away from the skin, keeping you dry and comfortable during your workout

fields.name: England Kit Shorts
fields.description: These Nike England Shorts have been crafted with Nike Breathe fabric and Dri-Fit technology which keeps you feeling comfortable by enhancing breathability and wicking moisture away from your skin. The shorts have an elasticated waist and drawstring fastening for a secure fit and the iconic team crest allows you to show your admiration for the Three Lions.

fields.name: Bibs (Pack of 6)
fields.description: The 6 Pack Mesh Bibs are great for your training sessions with the mesh construction for a lightweight and breathable design, finished off with Sondico branding to the front.

fields.name: Football Coat
fields.description: This Team Fall Jacket is crafted with full zip fastening and long sleeves for warmth. It features 2 pockets for a classic look and is a lightweight construction.

fields.description: This Team Fall Jacket is crafted with full zip fastening and long sleeves for warmth. It features 2 pockets for a classic look and is a lightweight construction.

fields.name: Ladies Cricket Bat
fields.description: This Slazenger V200 1+ Cricket Bat has been engineered with Grade 1 English willow, whilst the bat has a flat face with maximised edges which are rounded off to work together to deliver impressive power so you can make the boundary with ease. The bat has a mid-blade sweet spot which ensures great pick up and balance, whilst the semi-oval 12 piece cane delivers an optimal combination of power, control and flexibility. The bat has a hybrid grip so you can handle the bat with great control and the Slazenger branding completes the look.
